---------
SHORTCUTS
---------

W + z: Whisker Menu
W + Intro: Drop Down Terminal
W + A: Maximize window
W + E: Show desktop
W + right: Tile window to the right
W + left: Tile window to the left
W + up: Tile window to the top
W + down: Tile window to the bottom
W + x: close window
Ctrl + Space: Run Synapse



